Package: articulated
Type: Package
Title: Speech Performance Assessment Tools
Version: 0.3.1
Date: 2025-10-20
Author: Fredrik Nylén
Maintainer: Fredrik Nylén <fredrik.nylen@umu.se>
Description: Functions for assessing articulation errors and phonatory function
    from acoustic data, with emphasis on diadochokinetic (DDK) tasks and vowel
    space analysis. Includes rhythm metrics (PVI, jitter, pace acceleration),
    vowel space metrics (VSA, VSD, cVSA), and integration with the superassp
    package for streamlined acoustic analysis workflows.
License: GPL (>= 2)
